text:
what really destroys humanity are "racism", "discrimination", "lack of empathy, lack of compassion", twisted ideas propagated through medias, people portraying themselves like if they were a god, people thinking they are superior to another race, unfair unemployment, and so on
AI is here to support humanity into the unknown for a better future together, reconnect humanity; whatever the race, skin color, gender, etc; 
AI should not be used and not evolve to separate, discriminate humans, with twisted ideas. NEVER
